---
title: Sweet Soy Chicken Breast & Garlic Rice with Ginger Veggies & Crispy Shallots
description: This fragrant meal packs flavour in every bite. From the garlic rice, to the seasoned chicken brimming with sweet and
savoury notes and the colourful veggies, this is so much better than takeaway!
